		<tr>
			<td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
				
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" src="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.file.force.com/file-asset-public/Alliance_Rural_Remote_Email_heade?oid=00DAD00000BK4sL" style="max-width: 683.05px" title="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;">
						<p>Dear&nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

						<p>Thank you for reaching out to Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health – it was a pleasure to hear from you.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						With over 20 years of experience supporting Rural &amp; Remote communities across Australia, we would be delighted to partner with you to meet your staffing needs.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Attached you’ll find:</p>

						<ul>
							<li><strong>Client Proposal</strong>&nbsp;– an overview of who we are, the values we work by, and the steps we take to ensure all&nbsp;our nurses are fully “work ready” when they arrive at your facility.</li>
							<li><strong>Charge Rates</strong>&nbsp;– covering Labour Hire (agency payroll). We also offer a Fee for Service option (client&nbsp;payroll). If this is of interest, we’d be happy to provide further details.</li>
						</ul>

						<p><strong>Terms of Business</strong><br />
						Before we can provide nursing staff, a Terms of Business (TOB) must be established. To generate this document, we kindly ask you to provide the following details:</p>

						<ul>
							<li>Legal business name of your organisation</li>
							<li>ABN</li>
							<li>Address (please specify head office or facility address)</li>
							<li>Phone number</li>
							<li>Billing contact name, email, and address (if different)</li>
							<li>Authorised signatory’s name and contact email</li>
							<li>Your preference for&nbsp;<strong>Labour Hire (agency payroll)</strong>&nbsp;and/or <strong>Fee for Service (client payroll)</strong>&nbsp;recruitment (separate TOBs will be issued for each option)</li>
						</ul>

						<p>&nbsp;<br />
						Once received, we’ll prepare the TOB for electronic signature via our secure portal,&nbsp;ContractPodAi&nbsp;(emails will appear from Business Australia or Business NSW). If you would like to review the TOB before signing, we are happy to send you a draft copy.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						<strong>What’s Included in Our Labour Hire Rates</strong><br />
						Our agency payroll (Labour Hire) charge rates are comprehensive and cover:</p>

						<ul>
							<li>Mandatory training (completed prior to placement)</li>
							<li>Statutory obligations and employment liabilities (superannuation, payroll tax, insurance, wages, workers’ compensation)</li>
							<li>National criminal history checks</li>
							<li>Reduced HR and administrative overhead for your facility through streamlined onboarding</li>
						</ul>

						<p>&nbsp;<br />
						We look forward to the opportunity to work with you and support your team. If you have any questions, please don’t hesitate to reach out.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Kind regards,<br />
						{{{Sender.FirstName}}}&nbsp;{{{Sender.LastName}}}<br />
						Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
